 class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rjx1665702609708.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjx1665702609708.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjx1665702609708.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjx1665702609708\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Vertical Alignment\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Vertical alignment of the label— <code class=\"ph codeph\">Top</code>(default),\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Center</code>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__section_w1843ab1b5b1_w1844ab1b5_w1845ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__2\">Representation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Top</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__3\">Label is positioned at the top of the rectangle\n                        (default).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Center</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__3\">Label is positioned in the middle of the\n                        rectangle.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjx1665702609708__table_d12977e1_d12978e1_d12979e1__entry__3\">Label is positioned at the bottom of the\n                        rectangle.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjx1665702609708__section_s1b_jjk_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768034e141\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngv1688454370143.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngv1688454370143.html\" title=\"A label displays text on a component, such as the name of an associated field or an instruction to the user.\">Label</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702614021.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Labels in Forms and Reports</a><p>Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615643\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615643\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Vertical Alignment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Vertical Alignment Vertical alignment of the label— Top (default), Bottom , or Center . Value Representation Description T Top Label is positioned at the top of the rectangle (default). C Center Label is positioned in the middle of the rectangle. B Bottom Label is positioned at the bottom of the rectangle. Applies To Label Related Links Labels in Forms and Reports Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}